 r‚ÜêTest_ProfilingHappyPath url;key;Authed;Assert;res
‚çù Check the full profiling enable, read, clear and disable cycle
 r‚Üê0
 key‚Üê#.DCMS.GLOBAL.secrets.upload_token
 Assert‚Üê##.Assert
 Authed‚Üê{
     h‚Üê##.##.##.HttpCommand.New ‚ç∫
     h.URL‚Üêurl,‚çµ
     h.TranslateData‚Üê1
     _‚Üê'x-api-key'h.SetHeader key
     h
 }
 :Trap 0
     res‚Üê('PUT'Authed'/admin/profiling?on=true').Run
     Assert 204=res.HttpStatus
     res‚Üê('GET'Authed'/admin/profiling').Run
     Assert 200=res.HttpStatus
     Assert res.Data.on
     res‚Üê('GET'Authed'/admin/profile').Run
     Assert 200=res.HttpStatus
     res‚Üê('DELETE'Authed'/admin/profile').Run
     Assert 204=res.HttpStatus
     res‚Üê('PUT'Authed'/admin/profiling?on=false').Run
     Assert 204=res.HttpStatus
     res‚Üê('GET'Authed'/admin/profiling').Run
     Assert 200=res.HttpStatus
     Assert~res.Data.on
     r‚Üê1
 :EndTrap
‚çù Teardown: ensure profiling is off and data cleared regardless of outcome
 {}('PUT'Authed'/admin/profiling?on=false').Run
 {}('DELETE'Authed'/admin/profile').Run
